qm:



List all VMs:

 
 
qm list
Start a VM:

 
 
qm start <VMID>
Stop a VM:

 
 
qm stop <VMID>
Shutdown a VM:

 
 
qm  utdown <VMID>
Suspend a VM:

 
 
qm suspend <VMID>
Resume a VM:

 
 
qm resume <VMID>
Create a new VM:

 
 
qm create <VMID> --name <VM_NAME> --memory <MEMORY_SIZE> --net0 virtio,bridge=<BRIDGE_NAME> --virtio0 <STORAGE_ID>:<SIZE>,format=qcow2
Clone a VM:

 
 
qm clone <SOURCE_VMID> <NEW_VMID> --name <NEW_VM_NAME>
Change VM settings:

 
 
qm set <VMID> --name <NEW_NAME> --memory <NEW_MEMORY_SIZE> --cores <NEW_CORES> --sockets <NEW_SOCKETS> --virtio0 <STORAGE_ID>:<NEW_SIZE>,format=qcow2
Show VM information:

 
 
qm  owcmd <VMID>
Migrate VM to another node:

 
 
qm migrate <VMID> <TARGET_NODE> --online
Create a VM snapshot:

 
 
qm snapshot <VMID> <SNAPSHOT_NAME>
Rollback to a VM snapshot:

 
 
qm rollback <VMID> <SNAPSHOT_NAME>
Delete a VM snapshot:

 
 
qm delsnapshot <VMID> <SNAPSHOT_NAME>
List VM snap ots:

 
 
qm listsnap ot <VMID>
Enable VNC console for a VM:

 
 
qm vncproxy <VMID>
Attach a serial console to a VM:

 
 
qm terminal <VMID>
Create a VM backup:

 
 
qm backup <VMID> <BACKUP_NAME>
Restore a VM from backup:

 
 
qm restore <BACKUP_FILE> <TARGET_VMID>
Display VM console log:

 
 
qm log <VMID>




pct:




List all containers:

 
 
pct list
Create a new container:

 
 
pct create <CTID> <TEMPLATE> --storage <STORAGE_ID> --net0 <MODEL>,bridge=<BRIDGE_NAME> --password <PASSWORD>
Start a container:

 
 
pct start <CTID>
Stop a container:

 
 
pct stop <CTID>
Shutdown a container:

 
 
pct  utdown <CTID>
Suspend a container:

 
 
pct suspend <CTID>
Resume a container:

 
 
pct resume <CTID>
Clone a container:

 
 
pct clone <SOURCE_CTID> <NEW_CTID> --name <NEW_CT_NAME>
Change container settings:

 
 
pct set <CTID> --name <NEW_NAME> --cores <NEW_CORES> --memory <NEW_MEMORY_SIZE> --net0 <MODEL>,bridge=<NEW_BRIDGE_NAME>
Show container information:

 
 
pct  ow <CTID>
Migrate a container to another node:

 
 
pct migrate <CTID> <TARGET_NODE> --online
Mount a container:

 
 
pct mount <CTID>:/path/on/host /path/on/container
Unmount a container:

 
 
pct unmount <CTID>:/path/on/container
Create a container snapshot:

 
 
pct snapshot <CTID> <SNAPSHOT_NAME>
Rollback to a container snapshot:

 
 
pct rollback <CTID> <SNAPSHOT_NAME>
Delete a container snapshot:

 
 
pct delsnapshot <CTID> <SNAPSHOT_NAME>
List container snap ots:

 
 
pct listsnap ot <CTID>
Enable console access for a container:

 
 
pct console <CTID>
Create a container backup:

 
 
pct backup <CTID> <BACKUP_NAME>
Restore a container from backup:

 
 
pct restore <BACKUP_FILE> <TARGET_CTID>
